  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re:Flex is a game where you interact with multiple reactors that appear in time to a song.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They move smoothly through the mouse, so it feels like you're dancing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paran: Step in a circle to the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Triout: breaking triangles in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Han: Avoid explosions that go off in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vizet: dodge targeting missiles with blinks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple designs for each reactor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paran's cracks design causes shooting stars to explode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Triout's ether design creates three objects that defend against the vizet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy Challenge Mode with a variety of music and logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also an editor mode where you can play any song you want with any logic you want.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re:Flex is a game where you interact with multiple reactors that appear in time to a song.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They move smoothly through the mouse, so it feels like you're dancing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paran: Step in a circle to the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Triout: breaking triangles in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Han: Avoid explosions that go off in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vizet: dodge targeting missiles with blinks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple designs for each reactor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paran's cracks design causes shooting stars to explode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Triout's ether design creates three objects that defend against the vizet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy Challenge Mode with a variety of music and logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also an editor mode where you can play any song you want with any logic you want.</p>",
